OL,3,CGuernsey health bosses consider
OL,4,Cincreased charges to reduce deficit
OL,6,FAt a recent scrutiny meeting, HSC
OL,7,Fconsidered scrapping free
OL,8,Fprescriptions for the over-65's,
OL,9,Freviewing the subsidies for doctors'
OL,10,Fappointments and increasing the fees
OL,11,Ffor Accident and Emergency.
OL,13,FHowever, Committee President, Deputy
OL,14,FAl Brouard, was quick to clarify there
OL,15,Fare no active plans to remove
OL,16,Fsubsidies and any decisions would come
OL,17,Ffrom Policy and Resources, as part of
OL,18,Fits overall review of potential
OL,19,Fsavings opportunities.
