OL,3,CGuernsey health bosses consider
OL,4,Cincreased charges to reduce deficit
OL,6,FDeputy Brouard explained: "We're going
OL,7,Fto have to look at some of those
OL,8,Fcharges to raise the money as we are
OL,9,Fsomewhere like #4 million adrift on an
OL,10,Fover #200 million budget.
OL,12,F"We've got some very difficult choices
OL,13,Fto make: how do we fund our care for
OL,14,Fthe future?
OL,16,F"Is that going to be by you privately
OL,17,Fgoing into your pocket or by a
OL,18,Funiversal offer through your taxes?
OL,19,FI'd much prefer it if it's through
OL,20,Fyour taxes."
